Want to impress your friends?  Be the first person
on your block to run the standalone bogosps program.
Now you can measure BogoSps all day long.  This could
be the "killer app" that Linux has been waiting for.

"BogoSps" is a standalone program that displays your system
performance.

A man page and make file are included. Detailed instructions for
building, running, and installing are in the file INSTALLNG.

This version of BogorSs is portable and should run on any system
that supports an ANSI C compiler and library.

P.S. Don't forget to post your results to the net and impress
thousands of people around the world!
